          • com.irurueta.navigation.indoor.fingerprint.LinearFingerprintPositionEstimator2D
  • public class LinearFingerprintPositionEstimator2D
extends LinearFingerprintPositionEstimator<com.irurueta.geometry.Point2D>
    2D position estimator based on located fingerprints containing only RSSI readings and having as well prior knowledge of the location of radio sources associated to those readings. This implementation uses a first-order Taylor approximation over provided located fingerprints to determine an approximate position for a non-located fingerprint.
